  "content": "<p>2 ways to get local, Marketplace-certified help. Pick the way that's right for you. <a href=\"/node/39751\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"0fbe29a1-e92b-4b33-97eb-96b63c1b2274\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"39751\" data-entity-bundle=\"help_drawer\" title=\"Getting professional application help\">Learn the differences between assisters and agents/brokers.</a></p><div class=\"ds-l-row\"><div class=\"ds-l-col--12 ds-l-md-col--6 ds-u-text-align--center flh-panel\"><div class=\"ds-u-md-display--block ds-u-display--none\"><article class=\"media media--type-image media--view-mode-default\">\n  \n      \n  <div class=\"field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden\">\n    <div class=\"field__label visually-hidden\">Image</div>\n              <div class=\"field__item\">    <img loading=\"eager\" data-image-encoded=\"data:image/png;base64,\" data-image-width=\"642\" data-image-height=\"568\" srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_small_544/public/inline-images/en/find-assistance-flh.png?itok=uGz0sC0h 544w, /sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_medium_768/public/inline-images/en/find-assistance-flh.png?itok=N-FX-ubm 768w, /sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_large_1024/public/inline-images/en/find-assistance-flh.png?itok=vCr1HwY6 1024w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1290px) 1290px, 100vw\" width=\"1024\" height=\"906\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_large_1024/public/inline-images/en/find-assistance-flh.png?itok=vCr1HwY6\" alt=\"Find Assistance - Find Local Help\" title=\"Find Assistance - Find Local Help\">\n\n\n</div>\n          </div>\n\n            <div class=\"field field--name-field-spanish-image field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item\"><article class=\"media media--type-image-es media--view-mode-default\">\n  \n      \n            <div class=\"field field--name-field-media-image-spanish field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\">    <img loading=\"eager\" data-image-encoded=\"data:image/png;base64,\" data-image-width=\"642\" data-image-height=\"568\" srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_small_544/public/inline-images/es/find-assistance-flh.png?itok=IkcFGePn 544w, /sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_medium_768/public/inline-images/es/find-assistance-flh.png?itok=-wYHVsix 768w, /sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_large_1024/public/inline-images/es/find-assistance-flh.png?itok=zBPsMOoJ 1024w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1290px) 1290px, 100vw\" width=\"1024\" height=\"906\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_large_1024/public/inline-images/es/find-assistance-flh.png?itok=zBPsMOoJ\" alt>\n\n\n</div>\n      \n  </article>\n</div>\n      \n  </article>\n</div><h2>Find an assister or agent/broker</h2><p><a class=\"ds-c-button ds-c-button--solid\" href=\"/find-local-help/\" data-link-button-type=\"74921\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"c7fc1ad8-ecaa-4aa1-915e-2ba105f8c192\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"39976\" data-entity-bundle=\"link\" title=\"Find Local Help\">Find local help</a></p><p>Search our online directory and set up a time to talk in-person, over the phone, or by email.</p></div><div class=\"ds-l-col--12 ds-l-md-col--6 ds-u-text-align--center\"><div class=\"ds-u-md-display--block ds-u-display--none\"><article class=\"media media--type-image media--view-mode-default\">\n  \n      \n  <div class=\"field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden\">\n    <div class=\"field__label visually-hidden\">Image</div>\n              <div class=\"field__item\">    <img loading=\"eager\" data-image-encoded=\"data:image/png;base64,\" data-image-width=\"642\" data-image-height=\"568\" srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_small_544/public/inline-images/en/find-assistance-hod.png?itok=0LGwXW7B 544w, /sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_medium_768/public/inline-images/en/find-assistance-hod.png?itok=R6WCyP5j 768w, /sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_large_1024/public/inline-images/en/find-assistance-hod.png?itok=JXizHPz5 1024w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1290px) 1290px, 100vw\" width=\"1024\" height=\"906\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_large_1024/public/inline-images/en/find-assistance-hod.png?itok=JXizHPz5\" alt=\"Find Assistance - Help on Demand\" title=\"Find Assistance - Help on Demand\">\n\n\n</div>\n          </div>\n\n            <div class=\"field field--name-field-spanish-image field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item\"><article class=\"media media--type-image-es media--view-mode-default\">\n  \n      \n            <div class=\"field field--name-field-media-image-spanish field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\">    <img loading=\"eager\" data-image-encoded=\"data:image/png;base64,\" data-image-width=\"642\" data-image-height=\"568\" srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_small_544/public/inline-images/es/find-assistance-hod.png?itok=L72PHHDC 544w, /sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_medium_768/public/inline-images/es/find-assistance-hod.png?itok=61Phx_2c 768w, /sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_large_1024/public/inline-images/es/find-assistance-hod.png?itok=SxFJWDzq 1024w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1290px) 1290px, 100vw\" width=\"1024\" height=\"906\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_large_1024/public/inline-images/es/find-assistance-hod.png?itok=SxFJWDzq\" alt>\n\n\n</div>\n      \n  </article>\n</div>\n      \n  </article>\n</div><h2>Get contacted by an agent/broker</h2><p><a class=\"ds-c-button ds-c-button--solid\" href=\"/find-local-help/get-contacted/\" data-link-button-type=\"74921\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"dd6bb0d4-4225-42d7-ab14-07d958e5249b\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"39981\" data-entity-bundle=\"link\" title=\"Help on Demand landing page\">Get contacted</a></p><p>Enter your information and get contacted by phone or email (usually within the same business day).</p></div></div>",
